rc="https://ucarecdn.com/fc0a1a19-2e31-4fa8-a43b-9c408a123923/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Oleksiy.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="531" height="533" data-width="20%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="531" natural-height="533"></a></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1686564765807" data-id="1686564765807"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1700129794902" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1700129794902"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><b><a href="https://torokhtiy.com/pages/oleksiy-torokhtiy" class="" target="_blank">Oleksiy Torokhtiy</a></b></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1700129794934" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1700129794934"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="font-weight: 700;">Olympic Weightlifting&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: 700; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">Champion</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802779" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1662136802779"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Budget</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802785" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662136802785" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Just as the weight range, the price of an adjustable dumbbell varies as well. The price will depend on how heavy you’d like the dumbbells to be. The heavier it is, the more expensive the dumbbell will be. Which is why the Yes4All dumbbells are a good pick if you’re shopping on a budget.</p><p>Another determining factor is the design and technology used in the dumbbells. Fancier designs and adjustment technology will probably drive the price higher. So, when shopping around for a pair of adjustable dumbbells, keep all of these factors in mind, so you’re able to pick out the one that not only meets your exercising needs but your price range as well.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802783" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1662136802783"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Design</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802787" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662136802787" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Design can make or break an adjustable dumbbell. Some companies focus so much on the design that they end up creating dumbbells that are impractical. Or, at the very least, interfere with certain exercises. So, when looking for adjustable dumbbells, keep in mind the type of workouts you’re planning on doing, as they will help you narrow down the selection of which dumbbells to pick.&nbsp;</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802788" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1662136802788" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/91a846f3-1e22-4fe6-bc62-fe18ff87169f/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Adjustable%20Dumbbell.jpg" alt="Adjustable Dumbbell in Use" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="1200" height="800" data-width="800px" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1200" natural-height="800"></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1662136802786" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1662136802786" data-row-gap="0px" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12" style="display: block;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1658828961229" data-id="1658828961229"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802789" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1662136802789"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">FAQ</h2></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802791" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1662136802791"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">How Much Weight Can Adjustable Dumbbells Hold?</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802792" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662136802792"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">There isn’t a simple answer to this question because it all depends on the dumbbell itself. Certain, like the powerblocks, are built to ‌add extra weight, so they can hold more weight than others, which might be capped off at 50 pounds.</p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">There are also ones like the Yes4All adjustable dumbbells, which are made of steel and can carry more weight than others. While heavy weight adjustable dumbbells such as the Bowflex pair can go up to 90 pounds.&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802790" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1662136802790"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Do Adjustable Dumbbells Break?</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802793" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662136802793"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Yes, adjustable dumbbells can break. Typically, the material is strong enough to handle smaller drops, but if you ‌drop the dumbbells from a considerable height, there is a possibility that you might damage the shell of the dumbbells or mess up the adjustment technology built inside it.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802794" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1662136802794"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">What Weight Adjustable Dumbbells Should I Buy?</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662136802796" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662136802796"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">This entirely depends on your goals and how many years you have been lifting. If you’re a beginner, you can probably stick to the lower weight rang